desc: MamaLash Tania Gates is New Zealand’s International Expert Lash Stylist. Salon in Christchurch, LANZA Lash & BrowProNZ and WaxExcellence NZ Trainings. NZ Lash ICU - Urgent Removal Unit. In 2017, Tania opened a ‘Worlds First’ business, LASHES FOREVER, giving eyelash extensions to deceased loved ones.
